<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063843" n="1"/>
<opener>
<lb/><salute>Vir Celeberrime</salute>
</opener>
<p>
               <lb/>Ita pridem binas ad te transmisi <rs type="letters" key="B_1713-12-02_991170517055605501 B_1714-01-24_991170517055305501">epistolas</rs><note type="editorial">Briefe von Pietro Antonio Michelotti an Nicolaus I Bernoulli von <rs key="B_1713-12-02_991170517055605501" type="letter">1713.12.02</rs> und von <rs key="B_1714-01-24_991170517055305501" type="letter">1714.01.24</rs>.</note>, quarum res<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ponsum a te etiamnum expecto. In illarum priore
               <lb/>tibi significavi me frustra expectasse tui ad Mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matum <rs type="organisation">Cathedram Patavinam</rs> promotionem; et <lb/>me totis viribus allaboraturum sum pollicitus <lb/>ut ab hac Sereniss.<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Potentissimaque Republica</rs> ho<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>norifico stipendio ad eandem <rs type="organisation">Cathedram</rs> implendam <lb/>atque mathematicas disciplinas edocendas, advoce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris. Praeterea ut aliquam dissertationem Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">rum</hi> ac <lb/>Excell.<hi rend="sup">rum</hi> <rs type="organisation">Patavini Archilycei</rs>
<rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatorum</rs><note type="editorial">Von 8.03.1714-7.08.1715 waren die Moderatoren der Universität Padua Carlo Ruzzini (1653-1735), Alvise Pisani (1664-1741), Francesco Loredan (1656-1715)</note> Nominibus <lb/>inscriptam ad me transmitteres hortatus fui; in qua <lb/>potissimum theoremata ac praeclara problemata <lb/>aquarum fluentium velocitates, mensuras, modera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mina ec. respicientia continerentur. Rogavi etiam <lb/>ut aliquot problematum (quibus ad doctrinam missio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis sanguinis tractandam uti debeo) solutionem <lb/>mihi communicares. Modo ambigo an meae <rs type="letters" key="B_1713-12-02_991170517055605501 B_1714-01-24_991170517055305501">epistolae</rs>
<lb/>ad tuas pervenerint manus. Quicquid autem de il<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lis sit: impraesentiarum te admonitum volo, meos <lb/>pro tui honorifico delectu, atque non incerta promotio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ne, conatus indesinentes frustaneos haud fuisse: <lb/>siquidem brevi te eligendum, pro <choice><orig>Mathaesi</orig><reg>Mathesi</reg></choice> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> edo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cenda, ab hisce Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">is</hi> atque Excell.<hi rend="sup">is</hi> D. D. <rs key="pers_DE-588-1089924410 pers_DE-588-1111043582 pers_DE-588-1178371670" type="persons">Moderatoribus</rs><note type="editorial">Von 8.03.1714-7.08.1715 waren die Moderatoren der Universität Padua Carlo Ruzzini (1653-1735), Alvise Pisani (1664-1741), Francesco Loredan (1656-1715)</note>, 
               <pb facs="1063844" n="2"/>
<lb/>certo certius confido. <choice><orig>quamplures</orig><reg>Quamplures</reg></choice> etenim evici difficulta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tes; quae promotionem retardavere. </p>
<p>
<lb/>Statim autem ac fueris promotus atque electus, te cer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiorem faciam. </p>
<p>
<lb/>Interim ut quamprimum ad me mittas rogo sequentis
               <lb/>propositionis demonstrationem<supplied>.</supplied></p>
<p>
<lb/>Fluida quaecunque pressionem suam communicant per <lb/>lineam corpori continenti in quolibet puncto impulsus
               <lb/> perpendicularem.</p>
<p>
<lb/>Ut eodem tempore mihi indices depraecor: quam propor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem habeat fluidorum per continentia quaecunque 
               <lb/>fluentium, obliqua pressio ad pressionem nor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>malem in quolibet puncto impulsus.</p>
<p>
<lb/>Occasionem a te sciscitandi enunciatae propositionis 
               <lb/>demonstrationem, ex iis, quae <rs key="pers_DE-588-117689548" type="person">Archibaldus Pitcarnius</rs><note type="editorial">Pitcairne, Archibald (1652-1713)</note>
<lb/>scripsit, <rs key="biblio_EA3M6JGK" type="biblio">Dissertatione de Circulatione Sanguinis</rs>, 
               <lb/>nactus sum. Etenim in illa <rs key="biblio_EA3M6JGK" type="biblio">Dissertatione</rs> <abbr>pag.</abbr>
<lb/><choice><abbr>m.</abbr><expan>mea</expan></choice> 27 haec leguntur. <cit><quote>Demonstratu facile est (et demonstrare
                  <lb/>se posse ait insignis vir <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Jacobus Bernoulli</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli, Jakob (1655-1705)</note>) fluida quaecun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que pressionem suam communicare per lineam corpo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ri continenti in quovis puncto impulsus perpendicula<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem.</quote></cit>
</p>
<pb facs="1063845" n="3"/>
<p>
<lb/><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> Abbas <rs key="pers_DE-588-119291967" type="person">Fardella</rs><note type="editorial">Fardella, Michelangelo (1650-1718)</note>
<rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavio</rs>
<rs key="place_GEO-3172394" type="place">Neapolim</rs> petitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rus pridie discessit, mihique toto animo tui promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem commendavit. Id quod semper effecit <abbr>Ingenio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>siss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> et Amicissimus <rs key="pers_DE-588-119112450" type="person">Jacobus Hermannus</rs><note type="editorial">Hermann, Jacob (1678-1733)</note> vester, a quo nu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>perrimas accepi <rs type="letter">epistolas</rs><note type="internal">!-- ToDo: Brieftag in BIBB aufnehmen von Hermann's Briefwechsel vor 1714-03-10 --></note>, iisdemque hodie <rs type="letter">respondeo</rs><note type="internal"><!-- ToDo in BIBB aufnehmen: Brieftag Michelotti an Hermann von 1714-03-10--></note>. </p>
<closer>
<lb/>Vale, meque amare perge; et Clarissimum Patruum
               <lb/>tuum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Joannem</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli, Johann (1667-1748)</note> (quem magni facio, cuiusque sum aman<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimus) saluta, cohortare ac redde plane meum,
               <lb/>adhoc ut eius in sublimiori Mathesi inventa saltem
               <lb/>per litteras saepius delibare valeam. Is enim sum 
               <lb/>qui mathematicas omnes disciplinas summopere amat 
               <lb/>ac <abbr>colit.</abbr> <lb/><abbr>Addictiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Obsequentiss.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Servus 
               <lb/><signed><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></signed>. 
               <lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1714-03-10">10 Martii 1714</date></dateline>
</closer>
<pb facs="1063846" n="3" type="empty"/>
